ecotone/ecotone.name: ecotone/ecotone
ecotone/ecotone.description: Supporting you in building DDD, CQRS, Event Sourcing applications with ease.
Core modules for running Ecotone Framework
Ecotone is Service Bus Implementation, which enables message driven architecture with DDD, CQRS, Event Sourcing in PHP
Ecotone Framework is Service Bus Implementation. It enables message driven architecture and DDD, CQRS, Event Sourcing in PHP

Ecotone provides support for well known Enterprise Integration Patterns (EIP), to enable message driven architecture in PHP. On top of that follow an architectural pattern which is based on the principles of Domain-Driven Design (DDD) and Command Query Responsibility Segregation (CQRS) and provides you with the necessary building blocks to follow these principles
keywords: ddd and cqrs on top of eip

ecotone/ecotone.description: Provides a clean, elegant API for writing DDD CQRS and Event Sourcing applications on top off the well-known Enterprise Integration Patterns in PHP. It affords basic DDD and CQRS building blocks for aggregates, commands, queries, events, command handlers, event sourced aggregates, event handlers, query handlers, interceptors.

Provides a clean, elegant API for writing DDD, CQRS, Event Sourcing applications on top off the well-known Enterprise Integration Patterns. It provides basic building blocks for aggregates, commands, queries, events, command handlers, event sourced aggregates, event handlers, query handlers, communication buses and so on.
